00045 void CalvinCHPMultiDataFileUpdater::Initialize(const char *file)
00046 {
00047     DataSetUpdater::Initialize(file);
00048     dataSetIndexMap.clear();
00049     int nds=(int)dataSetNames[0].size();
00050     int ndt=sizeof(MultiDataDataTypes) / sizeof(MultiDataType);
00051     for (int ids=0; ids<nds; ids++)
00052     {
00053         for (int idt=0; idt<ndt; idt++)
00054         {
00055             if (dataSetNames[0][ids] == MultiDataDataSetNames[idt])
00056             dataSetIndexMap[MultiDataDataTypes[idt]] = ids;
00057         }
00058     }
00059 }

00125 void CalvinCHPMultiDataFileUpdater::UpdateMetrics(int dataSetIndex, int row, int startColIndex, const std::vector<affymetrix_calvin_parameter::ParameterNameValueType> &metrics, const std::vector<ColumnInfo> &metricColumns)
00126 {
00127         int colIndex=0;
00128         for (vector<ParameterNameValueType>::const_iterator it=metrics.begin(); it!=metrics.end(); it++)
00129         {
00130                 switch (metricColumns[colIndex].GetColumnType())
00131                 {
00132                 case ByteColType:
00133                         Update(MULTI_DATA_DATA_GROUP, dataSetIndex, row, colIndex+startColIndex, it->GetValueInt8());
00134                         break;
00135 
00136                 case UByteColType:
00137                         Update(MULTI_DATA_DATA_GROUP, dataSetIndex, row, colIndex+startColIndex, it->GetValueUInt8());
00138                         break;
00139 
00140                 case ShortColType:
00141                         Update(MULTI_DATA_DATA_GROUP, dataSetIndex, row, colIndex+startColIndex, it->GetValueInt16());
00142                         break;
00143 
00144                 case UShortColType:
00145                         Update(MULTI_DATA_DATA_GROUP, dataSetIndex, row, colIndex+startColIndex, it->GetValueUInt16());
00146                         break;
00147 
00148                 case IntColType:
00149                         Update(MULTI_DATA_DATA_GROUP, dataSetIndex, row, colIndex+startColIndex, it->GetValueInt32());
00150                         break;
00151 
00152                 case UIntColType:
00153                         Update(MULTI_DATA_DATA_GROUP, dataSetIndex, row, colIndex+startColIndex, it->GetValueUInt32());
00154                         break;
00155 
00156                 case FloatColType:
00157                         Update(MULTI_DATA_DATA_GROUP, dataSetIndex, row, colIndex+startColIndex, it->GetValueFloat());
00158                         break;
00159 
00160                 case ASCIICharColType:
00161                         Update(MULTI_DATA_DATA_GROUP, dataSetIndex, row, colIndex+startColIndex, it->GetValueAscii());
00162                         break;
00163 
00164                 case UnicodeCharColType:
00165                         Update(MULTI_DATA_DATA_GROUP, dataSetIndex, row, colIndex+startColIndex, it->GetValueText());
00166                         break;
00167                 }
00168                 ++colIndex;
00169         }
